   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Goma Volcano Child Protection &amp; Relief Fund</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">On May 22, the Nyiragongo volcano erupted, causing the evacuation of thousands from surrounding villages in Goma and more than 170 children feared missing.We will provide immediate assistance to children and evacuees affected by the volcanic eruption and already battling with COVID-19 in a region and armed conflict. Our relief assistance will include volcano awareness, food packages, clean water, hygiene kits, sanitary products, clothing, heavy-duty face masks, relocation and housing support.</narrative>
  </description>
